[
    {
        "content": "<p>What do you think about renaming <code>Inducing</code> and <code>Embedding</code> to <code>TopologyInducing</code> and <code>TopologyEmbedding</code>, resp.?</p>",
        "id": 462801754,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1723819614
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I agree they need to be renamed, but I disagree with your suggestion. Here's a list of my requests:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Make them be under the <code>Topology</code> namespace</li>\n<li>Make it clear they are Prop-valued. Compare to <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Function.Embedding#doc\">docs#Function.Embedding</a> which is Type-valued.</li>\n</ol>",
        "id": 462802019,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1723819724
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Or should I use <code>IsTopologyInducing</code>?</p>",
        "id": 462802026,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1723819730
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Hence I would suggest <code>Topology.IsInducing</code>, <code>Topology.IsEmbedding</code></p>",
        "id": 462802062,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1723819744
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We didn't use <code>Topology</code> as a namespace to be opened w/o <code>scoped</code> yet.</p>",
        "id": 462802111,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1723819771
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But probably we should (and move some stuff from <code>TopologicalSpace</code> NS)</p>",
        "id": 462802157,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1723819793
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"214703\">Yury G. Kudryashov</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/287929-mathlib4/topic/rename.20.60Inducing.60.20and.20.60Embedding.60.3F/near/462802111\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>We didn't use <code>Topology</code> as a namespace to be opened w/o <code>scoped</code> yet.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Have we not? I thought we had already moved some things in that namespace</p>",
        "id": 462802305,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1723819837
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Possibly, I missed this.</p>",
        "id": 462802459,
